<B>__{close shot reconnaissance car}
<A>__{maggio sits between the driver and another mp, both armed. (note: these are not the same mps with whom he fought.) the g company men cluster around the car, ad libbing greetings, kidding maggio, bucking him up. even the sergeants join in this; nobody likes to see a man on his way to the stockade.}
